  <entry>
    <title>Hyper-v + Ubuntu 折腾日志</title>
    <link href="/2023/08/10/hyperv/"/>
    <url>/2023/08/10/hyperv/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Hyper-v-Ubuntu-折腾日志-leaves"><a href="#Hyper-v-Ubuntu-折腾日志-leaves" class="headerlink" title="Hyper-v + Ubuntu 折腾日志:leaves:"></a>Hyper-v + Ubuntu 折腾日志:leaves:</h1><h2 id="安装Hyper-v"><a href="#安装Hyper-v" class="headerlink" title="安装Hyper-v"></a>安装Hyper-v</h2><p>win11家庭版中没有hyper-v，需要新建文本文档输入下面的指令</p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">pushd</span> <span class="token string">"%~dp0"</span><span class="token function">dir</span> /b %SystemRoot%<span class="token punctuation">\</span>servicing<span class="token punctuation">\</span>Packages<span class="token punctuation">\</span>*Hyper-V*.mum <span class="token operator">></span>hyper-v.txt<span class="token keyword">for</span> /f %%i <span class="token keyword">in</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'findstr /i . hyper-v.txt 2^>nul'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token keyword">do</span> dism /online /norestart /add-package:<span class="token string">"%SystemRoot%\servicing\Packages\%%i"</span>del hyper-v.txtDism /online /enable-feature /featurename:Microsoft-Hyper-V-All /LimitAccess /ALL<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><p>将文件名修改为hyper-v.cmd（包括后缀名）右键管理员权限运行，等待之后y重启</p><p>设置中搜索控制面板-&gt; 程序 –&gt; 启用或关闭windows的功能</p><p>找到hyper-v, 虚拟机监控, 虚拟机平台打开(可能会重启)</p><h2 id="Ubuntu"><a href="#Ubuntu" class="headerlink" title="Ubuntu"></a>Ubuntu</h2><p>官方网站下载映像文件</p><p><a href="https://link.csdn.net/?target=https://ubuntu.com/">https://link.csdn.net/?target=https%3A%2F%2Fubuntu.com%2F</a></p><p>用hyper-v管理器新建虚拟机</p><p>按照指示调整内存等(最后安装选项选择下载好的iso文件)</p><p>hyper-v管理器中关闭安全启动</p><p>具体步骤可以参考大佬的详细介绍：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/m0_52501802/article/details/129523710">Hyper-V安装Linux&#x2F;Unix虚拟机_呵呵哈哈哒哒的博客-CSDN博客</a></p><p>中间可能会出现<strong>please remove installation medium</strong>的报错, 没有关系, 如果没有光盘直接大胆enter</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
    <tags>
      
      <tag>奇怪的东西</tag>
      
    </tags>
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>hexo折腾日志(主要是各种配置)</title>
    <link href="/2023/08/08/hexo%E6%8A%98%E8%85%BE%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97/"/>
    <url>/2023/08/08/hexo%E6%8A%98%E8%85%BE%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <del>咱也没学过html,咱也不敢问</del></p><p>8.5</p><p><strong>url设置:cry:</strong></p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-javascript" data-language="javascript"><code class="language-javascript"><span class="token literal-property property">permalink</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token operator">:</span>year<span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">:</span>month<span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">:</span>day<span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">:</span>title<span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token literal-property property">permalink_defaults</span><span class="token operator">:</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><p>改为</p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-javascript" data-language="javascript"><code class="language-javascript"><span class="token literal-property property">permalink</span><span class="token operator">:</span> post<span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">:</span>abbrlink<span class="token punctuation">.</span>html<span class="token literal-property property">abbrlink</span><span class="token operator">:</span>    <span class="token literal-property property">alg</span><span class="token operator">:</span> crc32    <span class="token literal-property property">rep</span><span class="token operator">:</span> hex<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><p>就发生了一些奇怪的问题, 点击任何一篇只能链接到同一篇文章,改回来又正常了</p><p>8.11</p><p>今天进行本地生成时发现**Permission denied. You can’t use port 4000.**4000可能被占用了(似乎也没有开其他的进程), 总之就是换一个port就好了</p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo s <span class="token parameter variable">-p</span> <span class="token number">5000</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><hr><p><strong>插入图片</strong></p><p>这里还是来一个比较靠谱的教程<a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/265077468">hexo博客如何插入图片 - 知乎 (zhihu.com)</a></p><p>but</p><p>这些方法我用起来都不太行</p><p>最后只有祭出图床大法才能成功（网址在这里<a href="https://sm.ms/">Image Upload - SM.MS - Simple Free Image Hosting</a>）</p><p>直接登录上传，然后复制md格式粘贴就好了</p><hr><p>一般会遇到<strong>fatal: unable to access ‘<a href="https://github.com/Reductionreaction/Reductionreaction.github.io.git/">https://github.com/Reductionreaction/Reductionreaction.github.io.git/</a>‘: Recv failure: Connection was reset</strong>这样的报错，需要取消git本身的代理</p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">git</span> config <span class="token parameter variable">--global</span> <span class="token parameter variable">--unset</span> http.proxy<span class="token function">git</span> config <span class="token parameter variable">--global</span> <span class="token parameter variable">--unset</span> https.proxy<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><p>然后直接上传或者科学上网就好了<del>(总觉得这种bug是概率事件)</del></p><p>今天发现很久没有deploy的原因了:laughing:, branch里面main居然拼错了,多加了’</p><hr><p><strong>添加评论功能</strong></p><p>我这里使用的是giscus</p><p>1.新建github仓库</p><p>在新建的仓库中安装giscus(这是安装链接)<a href="https://github.com/apps/giscus">GitHub Apps - giscus</a></p><p>然后在仓库的settings中打开discuss功能(第二个选项打开)</p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/08/15/sDQ5BivKyNzRk71.png" alt="image-20230815213218073.png" style="zoom:67%;" /><p>然后在分类中添加一个Announcements选项(discussions里面新建一个)</p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/08/15/wZBNCyAfQxsXFbj.png" alt="image-20230815213439335-16921064811303-16921064844405.png" style="zoom:67%;" /><ol start="2"><li><p>官网中抄配置</p><p><a href="https://giscus.app/zh-CN">giscus</a>点击官网链接, 写好自己的用户名与仓库</p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/08/15/2Pv3sMo5LmtRfB1.png" alt="image-20230815213618496.png" style="zoom:67%;" /></li></ol><p>下面的分类选刚建好的Announcements</p><p>之后把生成的配置填进theme的_config,yml文件的对应位置就好哩(配置文件没有的可以不抄)</p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/08/15/EKkHwGygQJTWcLO.png" alt="image-20230815213802803-16921066847057.png" style="zoom:67%;" />]]></content>
    
    
    
